RecurringInvoiceCommentAttachmentForm is a Form
    is primary
    propagate as a drill
    title is "Attachment"
    Layout
        paragraph
            RecurringInvoiceComment
                display as text
        single column
            RecurringInvoiceCommentAttachment
                label is "AttachmentNumber"
                display as text
        paragraph
            visible when (HasAttachment)
                Attachment.Title
            Attachment.File
        paragraph
            Comment
